        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Hi friends \xf0\x9f\x91\x8b ,
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Happy Monday!
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         This is the last Not Boring of 2020. It\xe2\x80\x99s a look back on some of the things that have happened in tech and the markets this year, and a look ahead at what impact it all might have.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Looking back at 2020 personally, I am so grateful that I get to write to all of you as my full-time job. In a normal year, it never would have happened.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I can\xe2\x80\x99t help but think the best is yet to come.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Let\xe2\x80\x99s get to it.
        </p>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;">
         <hr style="background: #e0ecf6; border: none; height: 1px; margin: 24px 0; padding: 0;"/>
        </div>
        <h1 style="color: #1a1a1a; font-family: 'SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 2em; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;">
         <strong>
          The Best Is Yet To Come
         </strong>
        </h1>
        <div class="captioned-image-container-static" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">
         <figure style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="image-wrapper" style="margin: 8px auto; mso-padding-alt: 1em 0 1.6em;" width="100%">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td style="text-align: center;">
             </td>
             <td align="left" class="content" style="text-align: center;" width="332">
              <a class="image-link" href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVUkmOpDAQfE1xA3nB28GHVkvzDeQloTwFNmObrq5-_bjgMBrJyi2UGakMO1NhSfml91Rq9zZTfe2gIzzLCrVC7o4CeQpeY04kZaPqvB49lkx2oUxzBthMWHXNB3T7YdfgTA0pnh0IEdbd9UhmIywnjDOpZoWMsc6OHpCSxjNiL15z-ADRgYYvyK8UoVv1vda93OjHjfxqz_k4lMOWatxjcGlrpbCZBZqfobr727cxNd3I558roB9LSr7l8zrtOS0ZSglf0OqlAuyt46Ig7E3C3jTN2MM9oOG5B8SsdXLsrTG0H6mAXjEse-MtJRaEUHIcCh3MZn5SNM9y7dVmXLc4w3PJcobUC65AqJ4IjPqxnaSXs_S9U9xaYSkfMZ8k4t-CqGGPSxc0QQRhQjCmrAEDHmTllNvwexHP24i2hfx3lC7rmKpNOcSlwY-72WA9gbbR1Px2xFBfE0RjV_CXcPXS_5RyWiBCbv_CT6Y21ZFkTCHJBReXUE1ZwoWQGKmuMfvUuuI_0r9_xMIj" style="border: none; display: block; height: auto; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-decoration: none; width: auto;" target="_blank">
