          , has not been SPAC\xe2\x80\x99d (
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMtqxDAMRb9mvAx-xI8svCiU7gr9g-DEmow7iRNspUP-vspMoWBkCSHdqzMGhGkth9_WiuwMPR4b-AyPOgMiFLZXKH2KXhjplG47Fn0bhdOOpdpfC8AS0uyx7MC2fZjTGDCt-TnBudTs5jstlLbXK2-d5ABOUN66MI5RczF29qUb9pggj-DhB8qxZmCzvyFu9aLeLvKDHj7S6agZ14Wqr3PoM5Q7IFUVA-6VEqFUZ5WwTojWSmmEkBf1QUveJWfJSy65kFKQI8dNIxqHRpkhfU_2cWn5Msmm7gNtG--nDis-rzisJeWJ2vdbWGB-NujWnv5lzwmPHnIYZogvDPii-QTTT5ChEOXYBySG3GndcWes-TubOEljyS7vGCnHlabyv-gv0iSJsQ" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
