        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         This is how Silicon Valley has worked for the past half century, and the model that every new tech ecosystem tries to emulate: success begets investment begets success begets investment.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         With more than 250 live and announced SPACs, and an insatiable demand for IPOs of strong tech companies, there will be exit opportunities galore for companies that create enough traction and buzz. After a decade of increasing time between founding and IPO, I think we\xe2\x80\x99ll see that timeline compress. That will only further accelerate the acceleration, as new millionaires and billionaires invest in the next generation.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         It\xe2\x80\x99s not just the money, though, that\xe2\x80\x99s accelerating innovation. Entrepreneurs can now spin up teams comprised of the right people from around the globe and software that\xe2\x80\x99s purpose-built to handle whole, non-core functions.
        </p>
        <h3 style="color: #1a1a1a; font-family: 'SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 1.375em; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;">
         <strong>
          Cloud Companies
         </strong>
        </h3>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <em>
          <strong>
           For more, read:
          </strong>
         </em>
         <strong>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkM1uwyAQhJ8m3GIBNj8-cOilr4H42Tg0Nlh43chvXxJLrSqxcJgdRvMFhzCVepi1bEhel8VjBZPhuc2ACJXsG1SbomGS614MI4lmiEwLTdJmbxVgcWk2WHcg6-7nFBymkt8OSrkgd6Oj504NEJxjPR0djMqrm_CDBili4Geu22OCHMDAN9SjZCCzuSOu26X_uPDPdnJBX2rKU7ftfkMXHl0oSxPWNk-ocM0v73Uqbefqm06S4ZRTxjljvdBUdqzTKHvp09eknpeBLhP_9xup5jemyY-7W2B-C62cbe-y54SHhez8DPHsjSe-Nwk7QYbasEbrsEGjWoiRaqmkOns2MFwqpRkdSUuOpbnyX-gPtEiJlQ" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           We\xe2\x80\x99re Never Going Back
          </a>
          ,
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkM1uhSAQRp_mstMA_sGCRTd9DTPKXKVFMDDW-Pal16RNE2AWX4aT78xAuMR0mT1mYj_PSNeOJuCZPRJhYkfGNDprRC9V07WaWdNaoTrFXB6fCXED5w2lA9l-TN7NQC6G1wbnsmOrARSAAJ0d2qnVivfzc9AN15PQQqOEmwuHdRhmNPiF6YoBmTcr0Z4fzdtDvpcTIk0xubDU-ZgywfxZz3ErwV4u7C5X4H1FK1YnXJWNZ2DOSC65kFKIpivkWtSK-qaf3McynI-Wb4v89xtL5hdT4s8VNvSvoJQby9yO4OgaMcDk0d696db3MjEuGDAVrXYEKtK46jrNVT_0w92ziJH9MCjBNStkG8tW-IN-AzfLiRk" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           APIs All the Way Down
          </a>
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Geography has always been a rate limiting factor on progress. Now, after ten months of remote interaction, and with a wave of new, remote-first collaboration tools coming to market, it no longer will be. That is going to be an absolutely enormous unlock.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         \xe2\x80\x9c
         <em>
          When it is all said and done, I believe that historians will look back at the
          <strong>
           Coronavirus pandemic as the greatest catalyst for progress and creativity in human history.
          </strong>
          \xe2\x80\x9d
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Many of the most progress-rich periods in history were brought into existence by small groups of people in random places around the globe, like Edinburgh during the Scottish Enlightenment, Florence during the Renaissance, or Silicon Valley over the past half-century. Brain Eno called those flashes of communal genius \xe2\x80\x9cscenius.\xe2\x80\x9d Throughout history, scenius has been limited by whoever happened to live in, or could afford to move to, a given place in a given time. Pre-COVID, even with billions of people online, we didn\xe2\x80\x99t have the tools or norms necessary to capture the ineffable magic of IRL digitally.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Now we do. We\xe2\x80\x99ve lived through a global remote-first dress rehearsal, and while it\xe2\x80\x99s been bumpy, it\xe2\x80\x99s going to get better. I\xe2\x80\x99m convinced that this next generation of entrepreneurs will create the most fascinating companies that we\xe2\x80\x99ve ever seen, and do it faster than before, based on the simple fact that they have more potential inputs, in terms of tools and talent that they\xe2\x80\x99ve ever had before.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Take
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE1uxCAMhU8zLCMggZAFi256DcSPk9BJIAKno9y-zGRRybItWU_P3_MWYcnl0keuSN7N4HWATvCqGyBCIWeFYmLQTHLVi2EiQQ-BKaFIrGYuALuNm8ZyAjlOt0VvMeb0UVDKBVl1mNQwT9bxUc6jpWJmUvSsV545S2Hyt689Q4TkQcMvlCsnIJteEY_66L8e_LvVmo-YOp_3tpOoOeWUcc5YLxSVHesUyl66-LOMr8dA94V39XQVrX--RaTolNHlEtPSzs_V7rB9Du1t0-Z-poiXgWTdBuEmwjuYD6NZIEFpgQVjscVBlRATVXKU403QkLkcR8XoRJpzyE2V_k3_AKAnerk" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Hopin
         </a>
         , for example. The virtual events platform, founded in June 2019, is truly remote-first. It hires top talent from anywhere in the world, onboards and manages them in a process built for remote, organizes work around the things that need to get done, and creates its own, remote-first culture-building traditions. In the last 13 months, the company has raised $174 million, and it\xe2\x80\x99s
         <strong>
          already worth $2.1 billion
         </strong>
         .
        </p>
        <div class="captioned-image-container-static" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">
         <figure style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="image-wrapper" style="margin: 8px auto; mso-padding-alt: 1em 0 1.6em;" width="100%">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td style="text-align: center;">
