        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Cloud companies will be able to focus on building the thing that differentiates them, the thing that their unique combination of talent from around the globe enables them to do differently and better than anywhere else. They\xe2\x80\x99ll go from idea to IPO more quickly, and provide capital and guidance to the next generation of entrepreneurs, anywhere in the world.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         At the same time, employment will become
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkE1uxCAMhU8z7Ij4CQlZsOim14gIeBKmBCJwOsrtS2cWVSXbb_FkPftzFmHN5TJHrkh-x4zXASbBs0ZAhELOCmUO3vBBaKn6iXjTe66VJqHO9wKw2xANlhPIcS4xOIshp9cGY0KRzQjpnBsWNi2TBCG86kXvNFNslGq8a_nOtacPkBwY-IZy5QQkmg3xqDf5cROfrR5nWiOs197Vc6lo3Vfn8t6Mo3UKCSgWSL5S3CzSZ4iR1s0eQPNZqLPt1FJpSFQwwUkwTRgXgnOpNBs63mkc5LCExzo-bz3bV_EvhxSTMi65hLQ2-2uzO8SX0d6em-5nCnjNkOwSwb-J4Bvsi9G8QoLSgPvZYsPJtFIT08M4jG8CDZkYxlFzNpGW7HPbSn-hP_v3kWU" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          more liquid
         </a>
         . If software can handle a bunch of the time-consuming grunt work, and face-time is made obsolete, why not let employees provide their uniquely human input for 10 or 20 hours per week on a permanent basis, and for multiple companies? Or just give employees their life back? They\xe2\x80\x99ll save an hour per day commuting, and hours throughout the day not running to meetings across town, or waiting for the conference room. They could spend more time locally, with friends, family, and communities.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         They might even be able to work on starting their own thing, however small, on the side.
        </p>
        <h3 style="color: #1a1a1a; font-family: 'SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 1.375em; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;">
         <strong>
          The Passion Economy Writ Large
         </strong>
        </h3>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         When Li Jin wrote about the
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMFuhCAQhp9mudUAKuCBQy99DYIyunQVDIzd2Kfv7HpoQv4hDDN__m_yCEsup91zRfYSh-cONsGzroAIhR0ViovBCiVN23cDC7YLwvSGxermArD5uFosB7D9GNc4eYw5vSc4lz27Wz0L0XahHQwM3sw6SDP7TiqvYTLciMvXHyFCmsDCD5QzJ2CrvSPu9dZ-3uQXHS_UbzPlja6Si4GK4CTckOy-VrL9gCmnvJ30wqKVnP5JSe694aoRjUHVqjF-L_p56_i2yKYeY0U_PV57WbEp45hLTAu1H3e_wfpuUDBHdTtSxNNB8uMK4cqMF7o3BbdAgkJIg_NIwLjp-4EbpZW-MhIUqbQ2gg-MnEOmqfRv-gfORYPo" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Passion Economy
         </a>
         in October 2019, she couldn\xe2\x80\x99t have had any idea how prescient she was. With the benefit of six more months, in April, I wrote that one path for people laid off from \xe2\x80\x9cbullshit jobs\xe2\x80\x9d would be:
        </p>
        <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #67bdfc; margin: 1em 0;">
         <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0; margin-left: 1em;">
          <em>
           <strong>
            Passion Economy Businesses:
           </strong>
           COVID has shown many people the importance of having a skill that they can monetize directly with their followers and audiences. I suspect that we will see a proliferation of one-or-two person creative businesses like newsletters, podcasts, courses, design, and coaching. We will also see these business models evolve.
          </em>
         </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Back then, I had no idea that this is what I was going to be doing full-time. I thought, if I were lucky, it could be a side hustle that paid the rent and made me sharper. Somehow, eight months later, I\xe2\x80\x99m a full-time newsletter writer doing something that I genuinely love and having more fun than I ever thought I could for something I got paid for.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         And it\xe2\x80\x99s not just me. 2020 has been all about people building something, however small, for themselves. Over the weekend, I teamed up with
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM1uwyAQhJ8mHC3A4ccHDr30NRA2G4cGgwVLLb99SXyotNo5jEajbxaHsOZymj1XJO9n8dzBJDhqBEQopFUoNnjDJNejuE_Em7tnWmgSqn0UgM2FaLA0IHubY1gchpw-CUq5IM-uHIRgjPvRjU5K5dQDnJgmDV7Oil69rvkAaQEDv1DOnIBE80Tc6238uvHvfsdxDHuL1ZU9Onzksg1L3rpBguGUU8Y5Y6PQVA5s0ChHOYefVR23O91WPtQ2V3TL6x0ixaSMcy4hrd1-Pd0G8WN0Btt1ayngaSG5OYK_8PBa6QNsV0hQ-nreOuzbUC3ERLVUUl04nZ9LpTSjE-nNPvdU-i_9A5ISf_Q" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
