           </strong>
           and
           <strong>
            Shopify
           </strong>
           are public companies with market caps of $24 billion and $142 billion, respectively
          </p>
         </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Right now, there are hundreds of entrepreneurs building the next wave of creator platforms, opening up more opportunities for people to do their own thing while making a great living. Not Boring Portfolio company
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM2OhCAQhJ9mOBp-BPHAYS_7GgSkddhVMNCO8e2XGQ-bdLo7qVQqX00OYcnlMnuuSN7L4rWDSXDWFRChkKNCsTEYprgWsh9JMH1gWmoSq50LwObiarAcQPbDr3FyGHP6OCjlkjwNVeMs_DzNA1XAmOQ-CCeCc7xXo9P8znVHiJAmMPCCcuUEZDVPxL0-xNeDf7c5z7OL6QUVp7w1D5SuPU0g0XDKKeOcMSE1VR3rNCqhfPxZhvPR023hXT18RTf9vk2kmJTR5xLT0uTfp9tg_QiNwba7HSniZSE5v0K48fBu6QNsF0hQWnvBOmzdUC3lSLUa1HDjNH6uhkEzOpKWHHJzpf_QP_WZgFA" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Composer
         </a>
         , for example, will one day let anyone start their own mini hedge fund, bringing us full circle. We\xe2\x80\x99ll be able to make a living investing in the companies building the next generation of innovative products. The wheel will spin more quickly.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         As more people build their own audiences, distribution, and products, we\xe2\x80\x99ll become even more resilient the next time a crisis hits. Our identities might not be so tied up in our jobs. We\xe2\x80\x99ll have a way to pay rent without waiting for the government to agree. We\xe2\x80\x99ll have autonomy and control.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         This is the way the world was heading in early February, but it would have taken a lot longer to get where we are today. Now, after a wild, tragic, scary, inspiring 2020, there\xe2\x80\x99s more money supporting innovation than ever before, entirely new ways to build companies, and more opportunity -- and necessity -- for people to follow their passions than ever before.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         So apologies if this whole letter comes off as cheesy, pollyanna-ish, or naive, that\xe2\x80\x99s just how my brain works. I\xe2\x80\x99m unabashedly optimistic.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Look at us. We survived 2020. The best is yet to come.
        </p>
